commit.message:
91-sbctl.install: don't sign without signing keys

It's expected that signing doesn't work without having previously
generated keys, so don't try to sign when keys don't exist.

Closes: https://github.com/Foxboron/sbctl/issues/187
Signed-off-by: John Helmert III <ajak@gentoo.org>

commit.message: Add mkinitcpio post hook

Ensure file signing hook is run when initrd is rebuilt

Initrd is rebuilt when a DKMS module or firmware package is installed as of these commits to mkinitcpio:
https://gitlab.archlinux.org/archlinux/mkinitcpio/mkinitcpio/-/commit/aff81712789b9f2c1664fe1cfb5c1ecdbc5c993b
https://gitlab.archlinux.org/archlinux/mkinitcpio/mkinitcpio/-/commit/3576b03d29420ccd1913eaa18c7f8950e7de3103
